description:
"The Coming Judgments of God" Interview (3ABN Today Live) - On August 18, 2016 Pastor Wohlberg was interviewed by C.A. Murray about “The Coming Judgments of God" on 3ABN. The focus of the interview was: the character of God, His mercy and justice, natural disasters, and coming fireballs from the sky.
